description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Navigate Jetpack Man (and his friend Sonic Sid the Squid) through the mazes, avoiding the baddies, collecting power-ups, and eating whatever is in your way!  Play simultaneously with a friend as you try to make it to the Theoretical 4th Dimension!
